org.afplib.afplib

Interface TileSetColor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TileSetColorImpl

    public interface TileSetColor
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Tile Set Color'.

    The following features are supported:

    • CSPACE
    • RESERVED
    • SIZE1
    • SIZE2
    • SIZE3
    • SIZE4
    • CVAL1
    • CVAL2
    • CVAL3
    • CVAL4

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getTileSetColor()
